{"tid":730244,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"里昂發表報告 1478 目標價大降51%，至4.26元，評級「沽售」。","createTime":"2018-07-05T08:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T07:45:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c54b4ee4da6cc402b259a726d2526b24efa39a","tid":730244,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"丘鈦科技(01478)遭大行大削目標價，股價急跌9.2%，低見5.01港元，較去年8月底高位23.25元，股價不足1年蒸發78%。<br />\n<br />\n里昂發表報告表示，儘管丘鈦今年攝像鏡頭模組付運量按年增長24%，惟得悉旗下1,300萬像素以上產品的毛利率回落至高單位數。預期丘鈦上半年毛利率由去年的12.1%，明顯降至7.7%，將其目標價大降51%，至4.26元，評級維持「沽售」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=01478&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180705145257491-0705_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Frelated_news_content.html%3Flocation%3Dhk%26symbol%3D01478%26section%3Drelated_news%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180705145257491-0705_00842_001&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwu57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=44c035fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=01478&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180705145257491-0705_00842_001</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf75f34d9a0b23304d5fd2d2d7c7b919d6e3825","tid":730244,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"去年8月底高位23.25元，股價不足1年蒸發78%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1dde22879c50979b0f7acf4ba961d8a30a6539","tid":730244,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"Why your topic no star?"},{"pid":"8a3a0a466e27ddd743160a312cfbc4b9784a6095","tid":730244,"uid":19454,